{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ArrayBuffer","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/@@species\"><code>get ArrayBuffer[@@species]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/byteLength\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype.byteLength</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/isView\"><code>ArrayBuffer.isView()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype.slice()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Herança:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/arguments\"><code>Function.prototype.arguments</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>O objeto <strong><code>ArrayBuffer</code></strong> é um tipo de dado usado para representar um genérico, buffer de dados binários de tamanho fixo. Você não pode manipular diretamente os conteúdos de um <code>ArrayBuffer</code>; em vez disso, você cria um objeto <a href=\"/en-US/JavaScript_typed_arrays/ArrayBufferView\"><code>ArrayBufferView</code></a> que representa o buffer em um formato específico, e usa para ler e escrever os conteúdos do buffer.</p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/arraybuffer-constructor.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">new ArrayBuffer(length)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"length\"><code>length</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The size, in bytes, of the array buffer to create.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A new <code>ArrayBuffer</code> object of the specified size. Its contents are initialized to 0.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>RangeError</code></a> is thrown if the <code>length</code> is larger than <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/MAX_SAFE_INTEGER\"><code>Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER</code></a> (&gt;= 2 ** 53) or negative.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"Description","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>ArrayBuffer</code> constructor creates a new <code>ArrayBuffer</code> of the given length in bytes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"getting_an_array_buffer_from_existing_data","title":"Getting an array buffer from existing data","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Base64#appendix.3a_decode_a_base64_string_to_uint8array_or_arraybuffer\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">From a Base64 string (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader#readasarraybuffer()\">From a local file</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.length\"><code>ArrayBuffer.length</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The <code>ArrayBuffer</code> constructor's length property whose value is 1.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"get_arraybufferspecies_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/@@species\"><code>get ArrayBuffer[@@species]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The constructor function that is used to create derived objects.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.prototype_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Allows the addition of properties to all <code>ArrayBuffer</code> objects.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.isviewarg_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/isView\"><code>ArrayBuffer.isView(arg)</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns <code>true</code> if <code>arg</code> is one of the ArrayBuffer views, such as <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\">typed array objects</a> or a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a>. Returns <code>false</code> otherwise.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.transferoldbuffer_newbytelength\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>ArrayBuffer.transfer(oldBuffer [, newByteLength])</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns a new <code>ArrayBuffer</code> whose contents are taken from the <code>oldBuffer</code>'s data and then is either truncated or zero-extended by <code>newByteLength</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instances","title":"Instances","isH3":false,"content":"<p>All <code>ArrayBuffer</code> instances inherit from <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties_2","title":"Properties","isH3":true,"content":"{{page('en-US/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/prototype','Properties')}}"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods_2","title":"Methods","isH3":true,"content":"{{page('en-US/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/prototype','Methods')}}\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.slice_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.slice()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Has the same functionality as <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype.slice()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In this example, we create a 8-byte buffer with a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> view referring to the buffer:</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var buffer = new ArrayBuffer(8);\nvar view   = new Int32Array(buffer);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Especificação</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comentário</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/registry/typedarray/specs/latest/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'Typed Array Specification' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">Typed Array Specification</a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n      <td>Substituído pelo ECMAScript 6</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-arraybuffer-constructor\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'ArrayBuffer' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Padrão</span></td>\n      <td>Definição inicial no ECMA standard. Specified that <code>new</code> is required.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-arraybuffer-constructor\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'ArrayBuffer' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.ArrayBuffer","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatibility_notes","title":"Compatibility notes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Starting with ECMAScript 2015, <code>ArrayBuffer</code> constructors require to be constructed with a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/new\"><code>new</code></a> operator. Calling an <code>ArrayBuffer</code> constructor as a function without <code>new</code>, will throw a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a> from now on.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js example-bad notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// TypedError: calling a builtin ArrayBuffer constructor</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// without new is forbidden</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js example-good notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\">JavaScript typed arrays</a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>SharedArrayBuffer</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Description","id":"description"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Instances","id":"instances"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores"},{"text":"Compatibility notes","id":"compatibility_notes"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O objeto ArrayBuffer é um tipo de dado usado para representar um genérico, buffer de dados binários de tamanho fixo. Você não pode manipular diretamente os conteúdos de um ArrayBuffer; em vez disso, você cria um objeto ArrayBufferView que representa o buffer em um formato específico, e usa para ler e escrever os conteúdos do buffer.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/arraybuffer","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/arraybuffer/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Referência JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Objetos Globais"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer","title":"ArrayBuffer"}],"pageTitle":"ArrayBuffer - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}